reviewText: Buyer beware the Vanguard release is a washed out horrendous VHS transfer. If someone can write a proper review (not a movie review) of the Vina release would be much obliged.
this is a great movie from the golden age of movies from Mexico when they were full of enjoyment and fun.
esta pelicula es muy buena ,muy amorosa y eficaz para todos los que en sus tiempos le agrada ser romanticos se la recomiendo
